The electrolyte is responsible for transporting charge between electrodes and continuously regenerates the dye during DSSC operation [12]. There are three types of electrolytes: liquid electrolytes, quasi-solid electrolytes and solid polymer electrolytes. The I3-/I-\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
